{"tid":379720,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"與準顧問醫生青梅竹馬 朱千雪低調護愛苗：結婚通知你！","createTime":"2017-08-29T14:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T16:47:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97dd50ab2985a657ee676a9cc5814e08e0aef0d8","tid":379720,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"藝人朱千雪前晚承認早前與準顧問醫生男友Justin蜜遊新加坡兼見家長，不過千雪揚言有責任要保護對方，故不願多談，實行低調護愛苗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vqp7CC_kzlP_rz6ySvL82w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9MTE1MjtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh_Hant_hk/News/TheSun/0827-00282-008b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVqp7CC_kzlP_rz6ySvL82w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9MTE1MjtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh_Hant_hk%2FNews%2FTheSun%2F0827-00282-008b1.jpg&h=227c6f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪早前被指與圈外男友Justin同遊新加坡，前晚她現身活動時大方承認，並表示兩人相處中，感覺很開心，又自爆母親與胞妹也有同行，她說：「趁有假期去旅行，我哋識咗好耐，大家嘅屋企人都好熟。（兩家人係世交？）我媽咪同佢媽咪熟過我同佢。」<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她稱與男友自小認識，相識了29年，可算青梅竹馬</span></span>，問兩人是否已指腹為婚？她笑：「唔係，咩年代呀！（佢媽咪當你係新抱？）係世姪女。（你媽咪好鍾意佢？）我唔知，我冇問佢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://tc.sinaimg.cn/maxwidth.2048/tc.service.weibo.com/www_fei123_com/e8a112bdc9b18d8e5c6948a8ebd361c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftc.sinaimg.cn%2Fmaxwidth.2048%2Ftc.service.weibo.com%2Fwww_fei123_com%2Fe8a112bdc9b18d8e5c6948a8ebd361c4.jpg&h=ab62ea9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「大家相處得舒服」<br />\n<br />\n千雪坦言兩人雖然相識多年，但最近才開始聯絡，關係比較親近，又不禁大讚對方：「佢都幾好，依家大家相處吓先，我唔急。我唔想講得太詳細，唔係怕公司鬧，因為佢係圈外人，我有責任令佢唔好被打擾。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（點解最近會撻着？）大家相處得舒服，發展得好自然。</span></span>（咁仲要觀察幾耐？）觀察到夠為止，需要多啲時間，大家又唔喺同一個地方，唔想諗咁遠，只係要諗下次幾時見、去邊度食飯。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popd.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/09193701/call5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popd.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F09193701%2Fcall5.jpg&h=dbbd1b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盼給予相處空間<br />\n<br />\n問到千雪是否已封盤？她說：「唔識答，我知道係咩意思但唔識點答。（你要畀啲訊息其他追求者？）我冇其他追求者，所以唔使畀，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之結婚通知你</span></span>，順其自然。」她又澄清Justin是修讀Interventional Radiology（介入放射學），已經不是學生，好快成為顧問醫生，而且在外國工作，希望大家給予二人相處空間。"},{"pid":"6c2edb7c7a4a57122992f2384a6203868f07651f","tid":379720,"uid":17418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"咁咪幾好！"},{"pid":"51e950a4bb019ee869617ed786ad3257404d70a9","tid":379720,"uid":129273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.popd.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/09193701/call5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popd.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F09193701%2Fcall5.jpg&h=dbbd1b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚股揸咗仲諗住人地放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c9217f48e9529bccd890fd5230e7d3ea020618","tid":379720,"uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n靚股揸咗仲諗住人地放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i15.tinypic.com/ws9p3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi15.tinypic.com%2Fws9p3o.jpg&h=ebebf320&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d173b936fd50845ef5145ca345911acba53c8f","tid":379720,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"顧問醫生好大粒？"},{"pid":"f76989151dbc60f0bb2b82d431fd24eac59096e7","tid":379720,"